===Etymology===
From {{m|en|Mag}}, a nickname for {{m|en|Margaret}} that was used to denote a [[chatterer]], + {{m|en|pie|id=magpie}}, an archaic word meaning "magpie", from {{der|en|fro|pie}}, from {{der|en|la|pīca}}, from {{der|en|ine-pro|*(s)peyk-||woodpecker, magpie}}.

